1. *Pogrešan* je potez njegove odluke. (His decision was a wrong move.)
2. On je očigledno napravio *pogrešnu* stvar. (He obviously did the wrong thing.)
3. *Pogrešno* je razmišljala o tome. (She was thinking wrong about it.)
4. On je došao na *pogrešnu* adresu. (He came to the wrong address.)
5. Ona je imala *pogrešne* informacije. (She had the wrong information.)
6. Ona je našla *pogrešan* odgovor. (She found the wrong answer.)